flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Tenancy Created]
    B --> C[Status: Draft]
    C --> D[Landlord Sends Contract Email]
    D --> E[Tenant Signs Contract]
    E --> F[Landlord Uploads Signed Contract]
    F --> G{All Onboarding\nCompliance Met?}
    G -->|No| H[Compliance Blockers Shown]
    H --> I[Mark How to Rent Provided]
    I --> J[Mark Tenant Info Sheet Provided]
    J --> K[Record Deposit Protection Date]
    K --> G
    G -->|Yes| L[Advance Button Active]
    L --> M[Landlord Clicks Advance to Onboarding]
    M --> N[Status: Onboarding]
    N --> O{Active Compliance Met?}
    O -->|No| P[Compliance Blockers Shown]
    P --> O
    O -->|Yes| Q[Advance Button Active]
    Q --> R[Landlord Clicks Advance to Active]
    R --> S[Status: Active]
    S --> T{Action Required?}
    T -->|Serve Notice| U[Serve Section 8 Notice]
    U --> V[Status: Notice Served]
    V --> W[Court Proceedings if Required]
    W --> X[Tenant Vacates]
    X --> Y[Status: Ended]
    T -->|Cancel| Z{Cancel Reason}
    Z -->|Mutual Agreement| Y
    Z -->|Entered in Error| Y
    Z -->|Never Commenced| Y
    T -->|Tenancy Ends Naturally| Y
    Y --> AA([End])
